@startuml
title SpringBoot Starter 启动原理流程图

' == 简约专业风格设置 ==
!option handwritten true
skinparam BackgroundColor #F9F9F9
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ArrowThickness 1

skinparam ActorStyle awesome
skinparam ActorBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #D0D3D4

skinparam ParticipantFontColor #2C3E50
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #7B7D7D
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #BFC9CA
skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #F4F6F6

actor "开发者\n引入 Starter" as Dev

participant "SpringBoot 启动入口\n(SpringApplication.run)" as Boot
participant "Starter 模块\n(spring.factories / imports)" as Starter
participant "自动配置类\n(@Configuration + @Conditional)" as AutoConfig
participant "Spring 容器\n(ApplicationContext)" as Context

== 启动流程 ==

Dev -> Boot : 启动 SpringBoot 应用
Boot -> Starter : 读取自动配置清单
Starter -> AutoConfig : 加载配置类
AutoConfig -> Context : 条件匹配 & 注册 Bean
Context -> Boot : 容器初始化完成

note right of AutoConfig
  使用 @Conditional 系列注解：
  - @ConditionalOnClass
  - @ConditionalOnMissingBean
  - @ConditionalOnProperty
end note

Boot -> Dev : 应用启动成功，自动配置生效

@enduml
